---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner article-body">
      <p class="eyebrow">Privacy</p>
      <h1>Privacy policy</h1>
      <p>
        My MetaTrader does not collect personal data through accounts, payment forms, or customer
        dashboards. The platform is non-custodial: you connect your own wallet and retain full
        control of your funds and keys.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you email the My MetaTrader contact address, your message and address are used only to
        respond.
      </p>
      <p>
        Hosting providers may collect standard server logs such as IP address, user agent, request
        path, and timestamp for security and operations. On-chain interactions are public by
        design and recorded on the blockchain.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
